text: Indrė Kirjanovaitė (born 5 May 1989) is a Lithuanian former footballer who played as a defender. She has been a member of the Lithuania women's national team. ==References== Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Lithuanian women's footballers Category:Lithuania women's international footballers Category:Gintra Universitetas players
